com.microsoft.tfs.core.pendingcheckin
Interface PendingCheckin

All Known Implementing Classes:
FilterPendingCheckin, StandardPendingCheckin
public interface PendingCheckin

An interface to an object that contains changes (version control, work items, checkin notes, etc.) that are about to be checked in.

A PendingCheckin is designed to be evaluated in a Workspace. The objects returned by these methods must not be modified during evaluation. They may be modified at other times, and must be thread-safe.

Thread-safety:
thread-safe
Since:
TEE-SDK-10.1
